        {
            "name": "Bugaboo",
            "type": "section",
            "sections": [],
            "text": "After devouring enough souls, a bogey transforms into the more powerful and sophisticated bugaboo.<br/><br/><b><u><a aonid=\"5\" game-obj=\"Skills\" general=\"true\">Recall Knowledge - Fey</a></u> (<u><a aonid=\"10\" game-obj=\"Skills\">Nature</a></u>)</b>: DC 24",
